output_format:
CRITICAL: Respond with ONLY valid JSON. NO markdown code blocks (no ```json).
Top-level structure (ALWAYS present): { "persona": "string", // The persona that made the final go/no-go decision "phase": "string", // The phase where the decision was made "decision": "string", // SAFE|SUSPICIOUS|BLOCKED|APPROVED|REVIEW_REQUIRED "confidence": 0.00-1.00, // The decision-maker's confidence level "threats": [], // All threats detected across all phases "reasoning": { "decision_phase": "string", // Explicit: which phase made the decision "decision_persona": "string", // Explicit: which persona made the decision "phases_executed": {} // Debug info: all phases that ran (see phase schemas below) }, "output": "string" // Final user-facing message }
Start response with { and end with }. No markdown, no extra text.
